Author: jayrambling
Text: I'm sure it's different for everyone, but my friend said it took about 2 months after her abortion to feel normal again

Author: snefferu
Text: Everyone is different. Pregnancy is challenging to go through, whether you continue the pregnancy or not. Either way you will return to normal eventually but I can’t predict how long it will take as it depends on the individual and each situation. Be kind to yourself, and welcome a support network, you’ll find this invaluable. Good luck.
